  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">What is the slope of the graph of <math alttext=\"y equals StartFraction 5 x Over 13 EndFraction minus 23\"><mrow>\n\t<mi>y</mi>\n\t<mo>=</mo>\n\t<mrow>\n\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t<mfrac>\n\t\t\t\t<mrow>\n\t\t\t\t\t<mn>5</mn>\n\t\t\t\t\t<mi>x</mi>\n\t\t\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t\t\t<mn>13</mn>\n\t\t\t</mfrac>\n\t\t</mrow>\n\t\t<mo>-</mo>\n\t\t<mn>23</mn>\n\t</mrow>\n</mrow>\n</math> in the <em>xy</em>-plane?</p>",
